                  "summaryText":"\n\nNASA is close to finishing the X-59 \"Son of Concorde\" supersonic jet, which could revolutionize commercial flights by reducing the noise of supersonic travel. If successful, the X-59 would be the first aircraft to allow for supersonic travel without the noise and vibration associated with it. The first test flights are expected soon."
